/blockquote><br />\n唔係咁易架， 葉師傅<br />\nD腔唔似大陸佬D普通話一樣收9你線.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次都玩唔到，好失落<br />\n<br />\n好想問下班入境處職員，打100個電話70個要cut線，25個屌你老母個西，最後5個先開到齋，呢d係咩感覺"},{"pid":"4582f4d5f5e76b885265228086ac82134939a158","tid":336443,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"成日傾到問完名，話你上海咩咩咩，之後就收9線，我做錯邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9baf5f9bc415f45d40cb953b8ad1c6acb9cc4d","tid":336443,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日傾到問完名，話你上海咩咩咩，之後就收9線，我做錯邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾到問名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7cae0e40a7beaaf26187a24be056847bb8301a","tid":336443,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:43:50.000Z","msg":"要講普通話"},{"pid":"02794bd78c35510f340da04c47f580dbb7a6133b","tid":336443,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"我是習近平，有什麼要禀報？"},{"pid":"88d374eac079fa3de038123bd8b9324607f6f1cc","tid":336443,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日傾到問完名，話你上海咩咩咩，之後就收9線，我做錯邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾到問名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問名呢關其實幾難過<br />\n第一要發音準<br />\n第二，佢會問你係邊個字<br />\n<br />\n過到呢關後，佢講一大堆嘢<br />\n好多時聽唔明。唔同情境要唔同對答"},{"pid":"a38183bfca47c00b904c575780db9b8c14f308d9","tid":336443,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:50:30.000Z","msg":"其實俾人呃果班真係豬閪嚟，一係就報假案<br />\n<br />\n香港入境處職員會同你講普通話？用吓你個腦啦，雖然真係知道你班支那豬係無。<br />\n<br />\n上次我屌鳩佢一係用廣東話一係用英文，結果佢收我線。"},{"pid":"ff64518b4a186d589bb37d980799a7313ae3380f","tid":336443,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日傾到問完名，話你上海咩咩咩，之後就收9線，我做錯邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾到問名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問名呢關其實幾難過<br />\n第一要發音準<br />\n第二，佢會問你係邊個字<br />\n<br />\n過到呢關後，佢講一大堆嘢<br />\n好多時聽唔明。唔同情境要唔同對答</blockquote><br />\n會問你個電話號碼"},{"pid":"4549c95cbcb206857b334525551e7b0dad1b8212","tid":336443,"uid":70491,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實俾人呃果班真係豬閪嚟，一係就報假案<br />\n<br />\n香港入境處職員會同你講普通話？用吓你個腦啦，雖然真係知道你班支那豬係無。<br />\n<br />\n上次我屌鳩佢一係用廣東話一係用英文，結果佢收我線。</blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦<br />\n<br />\n講普通話目的就系要screen out 班香港人， 本地人唔系target,唔好浪費時間"},{"pid":"74299c587f4a5d04d2ed29347f97590fe3dec018","tid":336443,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實俾人呃果班真係豬閪嚟，一係就報假案<br />\n<br />\n香港入境處職員會同你講普通話？用吓你個腦啦，雖然真係知道你班支那豬係無。<br />\n<br />\n上次我屌鳩佢一係用廣東話一係用英文，結果佢收我線。</blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦<br />\n<br />\n講普通話目的就系要screen out 班香港人， 本地人唔系target,唔好浪費時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係話一班豬閪聽到對方只會講普通話都會當係香港入境處呀。<br />\n<br />\n過濾無問題喎，但有人信先戇鳩呀。"},{"pid":"5512377c343bb7d3552f7a624500d3a19085dfa4","tid":336443,"uid":83913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實俾人呃果班真係豬閪嚟，一係就報假案<br />\n<br />\n香港入境處職員會同你講普通話？用吓你個腦啦，雖然真係知道你班支那豬係無。<br />\n<br />\n上次我屌鳩佢一係用廣東話一係用英文，結果佢收我線。</blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦<br />\n<br />\n講普通話目的就系要screen out 班香港人， 本地人唔系target,唔好浪費時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來唔止見工，連騙案都俾人screen走"},{"pid":"38169b123058d7f21745e3df5cee36e3235b2e41","tid":336443,"uid":70491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"btw,我試過講到去對方同我對身份證果part,我亂吹一個，結果過唔到關，應該搵網上程式gent個身份證再講，轉頭擺我段錄音上來"},{"pid":"f40853a932999aedd920e41ddc2d9e1bdd909747","tid":336443,"uid":4635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:53:05.000Z","msg":"原來咁撚難<br />\n比人呃到都算有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ec7b3473dfd1b12950b48b834ff1ca31a50e40","tid":336443,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"而家見到+852字頭電話打嚟我都好雀躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9235df82f90a3ed6367b0331cb74a8c7c0a09760","tid":336443,"uid":126932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家見到+852字頭電話打嚟我都好雀躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街我而家收親d入境處電話都係歐美地區打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c8d51e5113d8e67aba8623c1c237f4f3d7ec43","tid":336443,"uid":8689,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"打過黎好撚多次<br />\n<br />\n我開speaker 係office 同佢傾 <br />\n扮到好驚 話自己係台北 出唔到境點算<br />\n之後佢叫我叫咩名 我話陳蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢應該知我玩9佢 開始屌9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCut左佢幾次線都狂打黎 問我係台北邊度<br />\n話帶埋成班兄弟黎幹我 一定會搵到我黎幹"},{"pid":"43fd63954ade946a296e589e5fb65559a75a4a56","tid":336443,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日傾到問完名，話你上海咩咩咩，之後就收9線，我做錯邊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\